{"tid":1248571,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［鬥長命 鬥耐性］邊個打響第一槍 邊個就係輸家","createTime":"2019-06-21T13:23:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T16:46:05.000Z","uid":265467,"like":64,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"021adde33b91268fdaaad228d6bca0acbc7c83af","tid":1248571,"uid":265467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:23:41.000Z","msg":"警犬士氣低落 急需人頭祭旗轉移矛盾  震士氣<br />\n<br />\n同樣警犬夠膽清場打出一槍  必定引發災難性遊行人數升級<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只家只要 鬥耐性 等警犬主動先出手 必定會成功<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">見到有人先衝搞事 一定要制止 後退切割<br />\n警犬主場武鬥0勝算  衝果d 100%走唔甩！！ </span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"27aa1bf5c70e28817fb10273dad7a7ef35f73dbc","tid":1248571,"uid":265467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:26:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"090a1f929661e1154df6a1804c1a100b43fc1ae2","tid":1248571,"uid":265467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:28:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd7cc7456b95ad6895ee284c0ac42728023bf1f9","tid":1248571,"uid":265467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:33:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e496934c3cefec9813cdfa6bea74a9a7f5753f99","tid":1248571,"uid":265467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:38:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7755b1f4873334b21d4a62079619cbfadf85c63","tid":1248571,"uid":132283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:39:44.000Z","msg":"開始入夜<br />\n大家小心<br />\n冷靜"},{"pid":"407247797cff56493ddc2d7a30014bbd3cf2c24a","tid":1248571,"uid":98431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:40:10.000Z","msg":"支持 烈士遺言 我地唔係暴徒<br />\n<br />\n我地唔洗自眨身價同佢鬥賤架!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認清目標 聚焦醫警濫權<br />\n<br />\n修例係撤回定停止已經唔係重點<br />\n<br />\n今日圍完 應該盡早散 僵持不下無意思<br />\n<br />\n國際人權組織已經出左報告 今晚有意外就前功盡廢了<br />\n<br />\n手足辛苦完 應該到宣傳組出場<br />\n<br />\n多謝各位耐心睇完"},{"pid":"a2d1a6cf21cafe82e127566a49f041deb6f3bde1","tid":1248571,"uid":265467,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:44:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bad881a0d46a12578b08840074b94e80927017cb","tid":1248571,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:46:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a422bb9650ff4e5e73c656fca203b2fbf4afc6","tid":1248571,"uid":36359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:47:09.000Z","msg":"冇錯 <br />\n所謂狗急跳牆 咁樣落去班狗總會失控<br />\n我地唔係驚死 但一定要逼班狗打第一槍 <br />\n到時我地就贏到開巷"},{"pid":"fb295357692d2f4fbcb15d840a33a54ff151b946","tid":1248571,"uid":265467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:51:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30917167ded0187512dda3462808e1a5fa293c0e","tid":1248571,"uid":264613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:53:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4551548459d2186de03110568a8ad9cffd8b4d6b","tid":1248571,"uid":263842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:54:36.000Z","msg":"只要一直守落去，唔好衝，俾借口佢地衝返出黎，佢地成4千幾人喺裡面，冇糧入去，遲早會斷糧，實行要佢地餓到一個點。"},{"pid":"28f6daa107d744776f2563f08f55d43aa88b8dc9","tid":1248571,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e87d425cd8f62b1df47358bf20bcbc094c9b7a","tid":1248571,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:00:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冷靜，唔好衝，注意時機準備撤退</span></span>"},{"pid":"da72fe24b057888238e3b7cae92550dd89f9f686","tid":1248571,"uid":265467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:03:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3662a9796b25b7d0abe9f0fb2aa91eb8c948761","tid":1248571,"uid":194609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:04:11.000Z","msg":"你和平：<br />\n冷處理消耗民意  <br />\n搵一日偷偷開會<br />\n多人抗議就再暫緩<br />\n少人就直接通過    <br />\n佢嘅成本只係一張通告就開會/暫緩<br />\n我地嘅成本就係每次要幾萬人出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你勇武：<br />\n我地政府警方都縮緊你都搞事<br />\n你係暴徒  佢地就出師有名<br />\n加上香港人善忘  <br />\n瞄頭開槍   圍毆倒地呀伯   圍困中信示威者<br />\n全部唔記得哂  <br />\n所以先會驚對方有位入   <br />\n人地向你頭開槍，但好多人都仲驚緊比位人入<br />\n<br />\n所以而家最好嘅方法係公眾唔討厭嘅「勇武」<br />\n但你一定要搞到佢  逼佢回應<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇撚穿哂   咪當我地傻</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712fda64cd3242ab8b10296f43302113dc61b76b","tid":1248571,"uid":265467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:08:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84973a1d2b7f887b8e9b541d147504d23cb4a2ac","tid":1248571,"uid":235570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:09:22.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"ddd5318d12f7360c98873f2462e1fcb801237f8d","tid":1248571,"uid":265467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:13:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"130565dbd734abd707a0a53bfbf09cf4d8bf0634","tid":1248571,"uid":265467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:18:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5545e76407b4151f7f66b8acfc30a1732e624bef","tid":1248571,"uid":264565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:19:35.000Z","msg":"推！不受傷 不被捕"},{"pid":"f82ceea7459e5defd5531ea3eb9205b5317bb52d","tid":1248571,"uid":265467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:28:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b35575946861d9206e27580a709ef6f48d7bfe6","tid":1248571,"uid":265467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:35:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8bea7338af036679a6e86977716d95660cef811","tid":1248571,"uid":265467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:50:24.000Z","msg":"推"}]}